  <refsect1>
    <title>BUGS</title>
    <para>
      The TSIG key is redundantly stored in two separate files.
      This is a consequence of nsupdate using the DST library
      for its cryptographic operations, and may change in future
      releases.
    </para>
  </refsect1>
